    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit. Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength. Diamond flat files are great tools for a number of projects due to their construction and strength</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio 3 in 1 Ultimate T Rex Diecast Cars Transporter Truck Toy (2 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Roaring fun meets high speed action with Kidplokio’s Ultimate T Rex Diecast Cars Transport Truck! This dinosaur toys diecast car transport truck features a fierce dinosaur design, an exciting car launch action, 15 inch long car slide and four brightly colored diecast cars to play with. This fierce T Rex transport truck is designed for dino lovers and budding racers alike, making it the ultimate transport truck and display case for diecast cars!</p>\n  <p>LAUNCH ACTION: This epic T Rex diecast car transport truck features an exciting launch action, that sends diecast cars flying into adventure</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>T REX TRUCK TRANSPORTER:</strong> 3 in 1 portable dinosaur toys transforms from diecast car truck transporter to car launch and slide playset! The playset comes with four diecast cars and with no assembly required, this dinosaur toys transport truck is ready to go right out of the box</li>\n    <li><strong>AWESOME CAR LAUNCH ACTION:</strong> This epic T Rex diecast car transport truck features a fierce dinosaur design and an exciting launch action, that sends diecast cars flying into adventure!</li>\n    <li><strong>SUPER COOL CAR SLIDE:</strong> What’s more, the top of the dinosaur truck transporter lifts open to create a 15 inch long slide; Simply push the legs down and lock into place for another exciting way for kids and toddlers to play!</li>\n    <li><strong>TACTILE TOYS FOR BOYS:</strong> Let their imaginations roar with this hands on dinosaur toys diecast cars playset! Kids will love creating lots of fun pretend play scenarios, while it also encourages eye hand coordination and dexterity, as well as hands on and screen free playtime with friends and family</li>\n    <li><strong>DURABLE AND SAFE:</strong> Built to withstand even the most thrilling prehistoric adventures, this dinosaur themed truck transporters are safe and durable enough for all kinds of active playtime and is easy to wipe down; designed with little hands in mind, this playset is suitable for children ages three and up</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/70201/undefinedKPL_dino_truck_car_carrier_parent.png\" alt=\"Roaring fun meets high speed action with Kidplokio’s Ultimate T Rex Diecast Cars Transport Truck\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPDT789PAR</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>CAR SLIDE: Open the top of the transporter truck to create a 15 inch long slide, simply push the legs down and lock into place for another exciting way for kids and toddlers to play</p>\n  <p>DINO DISPLAY CASE: When not in use, the T Rex transport truck keeps diecast cars neatly tucked away and organized until playtime can begin again</p>\n  <p>This dinosaur truck playset also encourages engaging playtime sessions where kids imaginations can roar! Toddlers and little ones will love creating fun pretend play scenarios, while also encouraging eye hand coordination and dexterity, as well as hands on and screen free playtime with friends and family. And, with a built in carry handle and snap close side doors, kids can easily tote this T Rex truck transporter to go for playdates, travel and more.</p>\n  <p>Perfect for both playtime and display, this truck is a must have for every little dinosaur lover. Buckle up for thrilling adventures, where the roar of excitement never ends!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit. Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength. Diamond flat files are great tools for a number of projects due to their construction and strength.",
